page.title: 13KEMPSTON FAMILY ORIGINS - 2
page.content: {DAUBENEY SCHOOL SURVEY}<407 returns> {A.PUPILS.}50% were born in Bedfordshire & 26% In Kempston. A further 5% were born elsewhere in the county & 16% were were born elsewhere in Britain. Less than 1% were born in each of the following: Holland, New Zealand, Gibraltar, Cyprus & West Germany. {B.PARENTS.}The main country of origin was England <78% mothers 73% fathers>. Other places of origin mentioned by 1% or more of parents were India <9% mothers 9% fathers>;Italy<2% mothers & fathers>; Wales <2% fathers>; Scotland <3% fathers>. The following had 1% or less of parents: N.Ireland,Eire,Africa Guyana, Cyprus, W.Germany, Poland, St. Helena, Pakistan, Japan, Canada,U.S.A. Philippines, Malaysia, Gibraltar,Iraq, New Zealand, Malta, Singapore and Sardinia.
